cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.NE, cs.DS

This paper is about convergence analysis of reinforcement learning algorithms, which is a topic closely related to machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also deals with optimization algorithms and control systems, which are relevant to cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves mathematical analysis and theoretical computer science, which are related to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
